(6.6\) Request inbox workflow \(GUI\)) Tj
T*
(- Request inbox UI is currently disabled by default in this alpha build for stability.) Tj
T*
(- If enabled in code/runtime, the flow is:) Tj
T*
(- Open inbox tab.) Tj
T*
(- Select a request and click Send.) Tj
T*
(- Copy requester address.) Tj
T*
(- Paste same address into verify field \(must match exactly\).) Tj
T*
(- Continue to Send modal \(recipient + amount prefilled; amount can be edited\).) Tj
T*
(- The verify step prevents accidental/misdirected sends.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Common env vars \(set before runnode/CLI\)) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_API_URL ? override API base \(CLI target\).) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_API_KEY, ATHO_API_USER, ATHO_API_PASS ? avoid prompts.) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_P2P_PORT ? set specific P2P port; otherwise auto.) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_BOOTSTRAP ? seed list \(ip:port[,...]\) to join existing network.) Tj
T*
(- ATHO_API_URL + wallet recent pagination can be used to pull bounded history pages) Tj
T*
(\(limit/cursor\) efficiently from the CLI/API.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Security essentials) Tj
T*
(- Every API call needs X-API-Key, X-User, X-Pass; keys live in Src/Config/Api_Keys.json.) Tj
T*
(- Local dev: HTTPS off by default; if exposing, run behind TLS/reverse proxy and consider) Tj
T*
(enabling HMAC.) Tj
T*
(- Protect Api_Keys.json and backups; rotate keys/passwords; use read-only keys where possible.) Tj
T*
(- For release artifact integrity, generate and sign release file checksums:) Tj
T*
(- ./.venv/bin/python Src/Main/checksum.py build --root <release_payload_dir> --out) Tj
T*
(<release_payload_dir>/checksums.sha256) Tj
T*
(- ./.venv/bin/python Src/Main/checksum.py sign --checksums <...>/checksums.sha256 --key-json) Tj
T*
(<falcon_key.json> --release <version>) Tj
T*
(- ./.venv/bin/python Src/Main/checksum.py verify --checksums <...>/checksums.sha256 --signature) Tj
T*
(<...>/checksums.sha256.sig.json --root <release_payload_dir>) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Quick troubleshooting) Tj
T*
(- Port in use: rerun runnode.py \(auto-assign\) or set a free ATHO_P2P_PORT/API port.) Tj
T*
(- 401/403: wrong/missing headers or missing permissions \(send_tx, mining\).) Tj
T*
(- Stuck tip / sync_no_headers: check ATHO_NETWORK and ATHO_BOOTSTRAP; ensure seed is correct and) Tj
T*
(reachable.) Tj
T*
(- CLI can?t connect: verify API port in NodePorts.json, set ATHO_API_URL, ensure API is running.) Tj
T*
(- unsupported hash type during mnemonic keygen: ensure dependencies are installed from) Tj
T*
(requirements.txt \(cryptography provides the SHA3-512 PBKDF2 path on Python builds lacking native) Tj
T*
(support\).) Tj
T*
(- falcon_cli/toolchain pain: use Docker as an easy path:) Tj
T*
(- GUI node start issues / stale PIDs:) Tj
T*
(- list: ./.venv/bin/python Src/Main/stop.py --active) Tj
T*
(- stop all: ./.venv/bin/python Src/Main/stop.py --all) Tj
T*
(- restart from GUI Node tab or via Src/Main/runnode.py) Tj
T*
(- Check live P2P behavior in:) Tj
T*
(- logs/mainnet/network/network.log) Tj
T*
(- look for peer_connected, header sync, mempool activity, and block acceptance) Tj
T*
